  <div style="margin-top: 16px; font-size: 0.65rem; color: #A0AEC0; text-align: left;">
    Methodology: Calculated by taking the 2025 raw metrics (Loans, Cash, Income, Expense, Profit) as a percentage of Total Customer Deposits. Source: TechCabal Analytics.
